name: GIFT CERTIFICATE
description:
*Various Prices*

Pick your preferred AMOUNT and FORMAT in the options and get a gift certificate that fits your needs!

Formats:

DIGITAL: You'll receive an email with a printable digital image of the gift certificate. This is the fastest way (1-2 days tops) and there is no shipping.

PHYSICAL: You'll receive a printed version of the gift certificate through the mail. You don't have to worry about printing it, but there is shipping and it relies on Canada Post's shipping delays (normally 2-3 days but can get crazier during the Holidays). 


The gift certificate includes a PROMOCODE to be used at checkout on the official Young Ghosts Clothing webstore (http://store.youngghostsclothing.com)

Cannot be redeemed as money.

*If you would like to request a different amount, please email us at onlinesales@youngghostsclothing.com and we'll be happy to accommodate you.
